## Python

Managed with [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/). `uv sync` sets up the environment; `uv run …`
runs in it. Lint/format is **ruff**, type-checking is **ty**.{% if 'pytest' in test_frameworks %} Run tests with `uv run pytest`.{% endif %}
The interpreter is pinned in `.python-version`.

{% endif -%}
